               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350406-name-188" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350406-name-188" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350406-name-188" type="surname" value="ALDERBERT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350406-name-188" type="given" value="ISAAC"></interp>ISAAC ALDERBERT</persName>
                  </hi>. On the 24th of March, I was between the church and Temple-bar, about half-past seven o'clock in the evening—I felt my pocket picked—I turned, and saw the prisoner with my handkerchief in his hand, which he was rolling up—I took it from him, and watched him till I saw an officer, when I gave him in charge.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350406-name-189" type="witnessName">
